@monkeydoodle, what do you mean plans? It's still being worked on, but AFAIK won't be a FS9 product. I've heard it's going to be FSX only.


@legendary_goku, did you install it in to the correct directory? PSS for some reason didn't have the installer check your registry to see where FS is installed, and you have to manually browse to it.

If you're sure it's there, I don't know what to tell you, sorry. It's working fine here. I did have to copy the two fonts over twice to get them to work, but just made a short flight around SEA and everything worked fine.
